          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">MRG Gold Buyers</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-400 mb-4">
          Coimbatore's most trusted gold buyers offering highest market rates with transparent evaluation and instant payment.
        </p>
        <div class="flex space-x-4">
